				<p>VMworld  2006 will take place at the Los Angeles Convention Center.<br />
					<GEO TYPE="US">1201  South Figueroa Street<br />
					Los  Angeles, CA&nbsp; 90015</GEO><br />
					213-741-1151<br />
					213-765-4266  (fax)<br />
					<a href="http://www.lacclink.com/">http://www.lacclink.com/</a></p>
				<h4 class="rule">Hotels</h4>
				<p>Please  make your hotel reservation when you register for VMworld 2006. 
					You will  receive an email confirming your hotel reservation approximately four weeks  prior to the conference. The  following hotels are available at the VMworld 2006 group rate. Please note that these rates are only  effective until October 6, 2006. Transportation  will be provided between the conference hotels and the convention center. Rooms and  rates are subject to availability.</p>
				<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1">
