				<p><strong>Please do  not call the hotel directly</strong> to book your reservation &#8212; your hotel room is  booked through the VMworld 2006 registration system.</p>
				<p>For more information, check the <a href="/vmworld/registration_faq.html">registration FAQs</a> or contact the VMworld 2006 Registration Team at:<br />
					Telephone: 1-866-405-2516 (US and  Canada)<br />
					+1-650-226-0830 (International)<br />
				Email: vmworld@eventreg.com</p>
