				<h4 class="rule">City Information &amp; Restaurant  Reservations Desk </h4>
				<p>A concierge staff will be available at the convention center to answer questions about local attractions and provide  printed visitor information for VMworld attendees. The concierge staff will also provide restaurant recommendations  and reservations upon request.</p>
